│ 559 /// 1) Discovered and mapped by a reverse CFG traversal.                            │
│ 560 /// 2) Visited during a forward DFS CFG traversal.                                  │
│ 561 /// 3) Reverse-inserted in the loop in postorder following forward DFS.             │
